{"tid":2079610,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"油麻地夾公仔店遭一名中国籍男子刑毀 損失1550元","createTime":"2020-06-26T01:54:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T02:00:52.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"606e0c8910c8dc5d20bfb95bdcd3085b798bea88","tid":2079610,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T01:54:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image2.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/9bb7491da405ca5acf1ca03c64e4c985/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200626/_2020062609180767476.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage2.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F9bb7491da405ca5acf1ca03c64e4c985%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200626%2F_2020062609180767476.jpg&h=c2541156&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n油麻地一間夾公仔店凌晨被刑事毁壞，損失約1550元。<br />\n<br />\n事發在今日（26日）凌晨約4時，油麻地砵蘭街101號一間夾公仔店懷疑遭兩名中國籍男子闖入並惡意破壞，現場玻璃碎散落一地，25歲姓羅的負責人透過店內閉路電視發現後報警。<br />\n<br />\n警方到場調查，經點算後，共14部夾公仔機和一部兌換錢幣機被毀壞，損失約1550元。案件列刑事毀壞，交由油尖警區刑事調查隊第四隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n據報指，這間店開鋪約9個月來，首次遭人破壞。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hd.stheadline. com/news/realtime/hk/1804858</code></pre>"},{"pid":"fdb5c84f62254445e5d75c15c5078653bc134f81","tid":2079610,"uid":129348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T02:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VFjS09U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVFjS09U.jpg&h=43814cda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【#71遊行 堅持五大訴求 反抗國安惡法】<br />\n<br />\n日期｜2020 年 7 月 1 日 星期三<br />\n集合地點｜維園集合<br />\n集合時間｜2PM<br />\n起步時間｜3PM<br />\n遊行終點｜金鐘添美道<br />\n*遊行正申請不反對通知書"}]}